when you wish to add images to the image slider on the home page, simple insert the img tags in the array children of the div 'news-snap-container' example below. 

<div id="news-snaps">	
	<div id="news-snap-container">	

/*inset images here*/
		<img  alt="image" src="/_media/images/image_placeholder_01.jpg" />

	</div> <!-- news-snap-container -->
	<div id="snap-nav"></div>
</div><!-- news-snaps -->